data.description: Welcome to your new home in the popular adult Community of Sun City! This captivating Gemini property offers a harmonious blend of style, function, and comfort. Upon arriving at the property, you are greeted by the manicured landscape, carport space, and a gated courtyard perfect for your gatherings. Discover a welcoming interior with a living and dining room, a neutral palette, and beautiful wood-look flooring. The eat-in kitchen offers built-in appliances, granite counters, a tile backsplash, and white cabinetry. The spacious den is ideal for an office! The main bedroom includes French doors, a walk-in closet, and a private bathroom for your convenience. Enjoy relaxing afternoons under the covered patio. Don't wait any linger! Come, see your new home today!
